        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "Grisantian pelt armor is immune to fire damage, and its Hardness is doubled against piercing or slashing damage. Wearing armor made from grisantian pelt also grants you a +1 circumstance bonus to your AC and saving throws against attacks and spells that deal fire damage.",
